    // Each block will be printed in decreasing order.
    // The blocks themselves are ordered such that the numbers in later blocks are larger.
    // This means the first block will contain numbers from 1 to k_block.
    // The second block will contain numbers from k_block+1 to 2*k_block, and so on.
    // However, we need to print the blocks in reverse order of their values.
